data.description: This home is amazingly located in the heart of American Fork!  Close access to I-15, parks and American Fork High School. Inside you will see that it is an updated cozy 3 bedroom 2 bath rambler that has a lot of natural light. Roof and solar panels had been recently replaced prior to owner purchasing the home in 2019. Furnace and air conditioning have been updated and verification can be found on the units at the property as this property was part of the restore Utah housing program in 2016-2018. A current appraisal as of 12/15/2023 at $418,000 is available. New sewer water main was replaced 2023. Sprinklers need to be reconnected, 2 car garage painted and epoxy flooring plus extra parking, RV parking/ storage possibilities. Appliances, refrigerator, washer and dryer are included.  Home has Xfinity wiring for internet, security and camera's.
